    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<strong><u>向好友发起挑战，在众多混乱无序的派对游戏中痛快畅玩！</u></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777790/extras/ebe80a5caca95917cff8f2d077c2f67c.poster.avif?t=1721377686\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777790/extras/ebe80a5caca95917cff8f2d077c2f67c.webm?t=1721377686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>在《Pool Party》度假村中享受欢乐时光！在众多体育和格斗游戏中独自或与最多四名玩家一起玩，为成为派对之王而战。自定义你的台球——选择你最喜欢的颜色和设计，然后与好友正面交锋。祝你玩得愉快！<br><br>这些台球不仅讨人喜欢，还拥有惊人的运动能力。它们在竞技场上快速滚动和弹跳，速度之快令人难以置信！此外，这些球可以互相踢来踢去，因为它们毕竟是球！你会惊讶于完美瞄准踢击所产生的巨大力量，足以将对手的球踢得满场飞。抓起球杆，加入派对吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777790/extras/de1f0062cc325105f9d4980d7f9ff008.poster.avif?t=1721377686\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777790/extras/de1f0062cc325105f9d4980d7f9ff008.webm?t=1721377686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>特色：</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>混乱无序的物理类体育和格斗游戏<br></li><li>单人游戏或在本地多人游戏中与最多4名玩家一起玩<br></li><li>添加机器人以充实团队或练习技能<br></li><li>易学难精。任何人都可以加入这场狂欢！<br></li><li>台球、神像、相扑和混战等多种游戏模式</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777790/extras/b386139ecad5fc4e54cae85a0d56a5a9.webp?t=1721377686\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777790/extras/b386139ecad5fc4e54cae85a0d56a5a9.poster.avif?t=1721377686\" class=\"bb_img\" width=560 height=240 /></picture></span><br><br><strong>台球：</strong>将己方颜色的球踢进敞开的洞中即可得分，但要小心别自己掉进去了！<br><br><strong>网球：</strong>无论是单打还是双打，将球踢过球场即可得分！<br><br><strong>相扑：</strong>禁止踢击！通过滚动撞向其他玩家来将他们推入水中。要么推，要么被推！<br><br><strong>足球：</strong>每支球队有一名或两名球员，将球射入对方球门即可得分，或将对手踢开，扫清通往球门的道路。<br><br><strong>神像：</strong>争相拿起并抓住一个小神像。抓住神像即可得分，但要注意：抓住神像意味着你不能滚动，而对手会追击你，将神像从你的手中击落。<br><br><strong>厄运当头：</strong>有个玩家被诅咒了！踢、推或击打其他玩家，将诅咒传递给他们。计时结束时，被诅咒的玩家就输了，诅咒会找到一个新的目标。坚持到最后的人获胜！<br><br><strong>混战：</strong>将对手推入洞中，努力坚持到最后。<br><br><strong>锦标赛：</strong>体验各种不同游戏模式的组合，成为《Pool Party》的终极冠军！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777790/extras/e5ba0bbcf7bd76a6cf2d8ccdcb187f2e.poster.avif?t=1721377686\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777790/extras/e5ba0bbcf7bd76a6cf2d8ccdcb187f2e.webm?t=1721377686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777790/extras/e5ba0bbcf7bd76a6cf2d8ccdcb187f2e.mp4?t=1721377686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
